00:28:01.940 --> 00:28:02.850
facility.

00:28:02.850 --> 00:28:06.400
And, so, I didn't know anything
about the internals of NASA,

00:28:06.400 --> 00:28:10.400
so I just assumed-- I just
said, well, big federally funded

00:28:10.400 --> 00:28:12.950
research facility, big federally
funded research facility.

00:28:12.950 --> 00:28:15.880
I'm just going to use the
