00:35:16.657 --> 00:35:18.240
I don't know why
she's a woman anymore

00:35:18.240 --> 00:35:20.850
than I know why you know the
director of NASA's a man.

00:35:20.850 --> 00:35:23.650
It's just, OK, thanks brain.

