to be backed out and redone.

00:35:55.136 --> 00:35:56.760
I tend to think
things-- it worked out.

00:35:56.760 --> 00:35:58.270
"The Martian" went
really smoothly.

00:35:58.270 --> 00:36:00.735
I'm learning that was
abnormally smoothly,

00:36:00.735 --> 00:36:02.360
