00:36:56.840 --> 00:36:58.280
ANDY WEIR: Well,
I guess I'd want

00:36:58.280 --> 00:37:02.030
to be somewhere that had
a decent amount of water

00:37:02.030 --> 00:37:05.070
in the soil.

00:37:05.070 --> 00:37:08.770
So one fun thing that
happened is in the book,

00:37:08.770 --> 00:37:11.920
we see this huge long process
