00:38:10.410 --> 00:38:12.460
I'm saying
[? Assideliaplonessia ?]

00:38:12.460 --> 00:38:14.460
is a desert, and it doesn't
have a lot of water.

00:38:14.460 --> 00:38:16.370
And yet can't prove me
wrong until somebody

00:38:16.370 --> 00:38:19.460
