00:38:36.160 --> 00:38:40.840
ANDY WEIR: Yes and I have-- I've
heard all sorts of conflicting

00:38:40.840 --> 00:38:41.980
crap about perchlorates.

00:38:41.980 --> 00:38:45.000
I get people-- I get
some people telling me.

00:38:45.000 --> 00:38:46.940
So for those who don't know.

00:38:46.940 --> 00:38:50.200
For those of you who don't know
the details of Martian soil

00:38:50.200 --> 00:38:51.951
sciences.

00:38:51.951 --> 00:38:53.575
Martian soil has a
lot of perchlorates.

00:38:53.575 --> 00:38:56.180
