00:38:59.520 --> 00:39:01.680
Or so I'm told.

00:39:01.680 --> 00:39:03.390
I get conflicting
reports on that.

00:39:03.390 --> 00:39:06.300
Some people tell me, oh no, if
you grow plants in Martian soil

00:39:06.300 --> 00:39:08.320
without clearing out
the perchlorates,

00:39:08.320 --> 00:39:10.170
your bone-- those
plants are bad for you.

00:39:10.170 --> 00:39:13.200
Other people are like, yeah it's
bad for you, but so is smoking.

00:39:13.200 --> 00:39:16.510
And it's not as bad
for you as starving.

00:39:16.510 --> 00:39:18.380
So I get conflicting
reports on that.

00:39:18.380 --> 00:39:19.900
In an emergency situation.

00:39:19.900 --> 00:39:22.180
I think the perchlorates
aren't that big a deal.

00:39:22.180 --> 00:39:24.892
But you wouldn't want to
found a colony based on this.

