work and writing?

00:47:14.160 --> 00:47:16.800
Obviously one's-- their
both fueled our passion,

00:47:16.800 --> 00:47:18.846
so you make time for that, but--

00:47:18.846 --> 00:47:20.470
ANDY WEIR: Part of
it that really helps

00:47:20.470 --> 00:47:23.340
